24. Nxf5 $1 gxf5 25. exf5 $16 {with tremendous compensation for the piece as
indicated by Adorjan.}) 23... Rxe6 {and the game ended in a draw.}) 23. Na5 b6
24. Nb7 {Trying to prevent ...Nc5.} Bf8 25. Ke2 Rxa3 26. Rhc1 Nc5 27. Bb4 Ra6
