diagonal. For once, the g7-bishop proved useful after} 19... Nc3 {White
decided eliminating Black's counterplay and fighting back for the initiative
with} 20. Rxc3 $5 Bxc3 21. Ne4 {Your move.} Rxe4 $3 {[#] Black rightly answers
